      <h3>Grammatik (vereinfachte Form)</h3>
      <pre>
      START -> 'program' PROGRAM 'program-end' START

      PROGRAM -> 'write' ADDRESS ':=' EXPRESSION PROGRAM
              | 'goto-if' EXPRESSION OPERATOR EXPRESSION ',' ADDRESS PROGRAM
              | 'goto' ADDRESS PROGRAM

      ADDRESS -> '[' NUMBER ']'
      EXPRESSION -> '"' STRING '"' | NUMBER | ADDRESS
      OPERATOR -> '=' | '<' | '<=' | '>' | '>='
      </pre>